data.description: Welcome home! This exceptional property boasts brand new laminate floors, The stunning aesthetics of the floor seamlessly blend with any style of decor, offering a perfect canvas for your personal touch.  While looking great, this home also promises peace of mind with its long-lasting architectural shingle roof, which has over eight years of life left.     Head to the backyard, and you'll find a delightful surprise waiting for you. Right outside your screened-in porch, there’s a playground, perfect for creating memories with loved ones. Whether you're looking for your first home, a long term investment, or just looking for a place to call your own, this property checks all the boxes.     Don't miss your chance to own this gem!
